    <item>
      <title>Why the West can&#39;t see the genocide it enables</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/why-the-west-cant-see-the-genocide-it-enables/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 12:33:07 +0300</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/why-the-west-cant-see-the-genocide-it-enables/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;image component image-fullbleed body-copy-wide nr-scroll-animation nr-scroll-animation--on image-big&#34;&gt;  &lt;div class=&#34;component-content&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;image-sharesheet&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;image image-load image-asset image-642e0b3a9e36c8ab13f47f076d452c78&#34; id=&#34;lht642e0b3a9e36c8ab13f47f076d452c78&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;picture  class=&#34;picture&#34;&gt;&#xA;          &lt;img class=&#34;picture-image&#34; data-src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/west-enables-genocide.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Photo: European Parliament/Flickr/EP © CC-BY-4.0. Composite: Ariana Yekrangi.&#34;  /&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/picture&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;image-description&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;div class=&#34;image-caption&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Photo: European Parliament/Flickr/EP © CC-BY-4.0. Composite: Ariana Yekrangi.&#xA;      &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Are you watching? Or have the architects of this slaughter successfully dulled your senses? Israel is executing a mass murder of Palestinians before our eyes — an extermination campaign broadcast globally, yet met with the deliberate silence and material support of its European and American patrons. Executed by Israeli soldiers with the detachment of a video game, the assault has transformed the very texture of Gaza — entire neighbourhoods pulverised into vast fields of debris, visible even from space.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
